Template: r7mdaserver/mda-ssl-cert
Type: string
Default: /full-path-to/certificate.pem
Description: Certificate filename for MDA server:
 (If the certificate file is not found, a self-signed certificate will be generated.)

Template: r7mdaserver/mda-ssl-key
Type: string
Default: /full-path-to/key.pem
Description: Key filename for MDA server:
 (If the key file is not found, a self-signed certificate will be generated.)

